## Summary
Amplitude's Insights feature provides anomaly detection alerts for metrics using Prophet machine learning, allowing users to set up automatic, custom, and smart alerts that can be delivered via email or Slack, with specific conditions for triggering notifications based on confidence intervals and statistical significance.

